<li id="menu-item-21620" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-21620"><a title="gambling-license" href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/gambling-license/">ギャンブルライセンス</a>
<ul class="sub-menu">
	<li id="menu-item-22529" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22529"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/gambling-license/">ギャンブルライセンス</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-22532" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22532"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/gambling-regulations-in-europe/">ヨーロッパのギャンブル規制</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="menu-item-21621" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-21621"><a title="forex-license" href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/forex-license/">外国為替ライセンス</a>
<ul class="sub-menu">
	<li id="menu-item-22534" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22534"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/forex-license/">外国為替ライセンス</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-22537" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22537"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/forex-regulations/">外国為替取引規制</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="menu-item-21622" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-21622"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/emi-psp-license/">EMI/PSPライセンス</a>
<ul class="sub-menu">
	<li id="menu-item-22538" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22538"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/emi-psp-license/">EMI/PSPライセンス</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-22539" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22539"><a href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/emi-regulations-in-europe/">ヨーロッパの emi 規制</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li id="menu-item-22523" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-22523"><a title="BANK" href="https://regulatedunitedeurope.com/jp/bank-account-opening/">銀行</a></li>
